Title: Seeking Expert Advice
Description: Take this spool to Moratari. Perhaps she can make sense of this relic.
RewardText:
What do you have there? This artifact is absolutely radiating with temporal power!

<Moratari leans in for a closer look.>

Aha! Even more brilliant than I thought! Assimilating the latent temporal signatures of unraveled causalities...

Sorry, I am getting ahead of myself. Allow me to explain.
